#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/08a_Return_to_Kerlath.cfg:358
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/09a_Vengeance.cfg:92
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/09a_Vengeance.cfg:448
